Mike,

*IF* it hasn't been removed by some evil PO, then front of the trans on 
the drivers side.  Flat braided metal about 1" across and maybe 8" 
long or so bolted to the tranny and then to the frame.

First thing I always take off on a "new" vehicle and wire brush and 
retighten.

Cheers, dave

